text:
1 in 50 women experience an ectopic pregnancy.

Now is the time for the Senate to codify Roe v. Wade into law so that every American in every state has equal access to basic, necessary healthcare—regardless of their skin color, zip code or income.

Illinois and many states remain a safe haven for abortions, birth control and reproductive care.

This website can help you find and access the care you need: https://t.co/2NreAedmRZ.
